    "updated_at": "2017-04-30T16:23:03Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For (b) (and possibly (a)) I'd say, let it break. I think the main reason that OpenRA moved from Mod selector to Game.Mod style of launch is to let breaking happen and let the mods update their mods on their own schedule. I think upstream OpenRA development and changes shouldn't be prevented by mods."
